						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Dwedit wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">What do you need the blank tiles for, when you can simply disable rendering backgrounds, but keep rendering sprites?</div><br />This. Since sprites can be hidden with 8 high priority sprites, it's perfectly possible to hide both BG and sprites without disabling graphics and without wasting a CHR-ROM page with blank patterns.</div>

